messages.content: hola
messages.speaker: BLUFOR_english_PRIVATE_Autorifleman-1hGanXhhpro

messages.content: Hey there, how can I assist you?
messages.speaker: CIVILIAN_english_civilian_AidWorker(Cargo)-BZNtKP1HXIY

messages.content: I just wondered where you are from
messages.speaker: BLUFOR_english_PRIVATE_Autorifleman-1hGanXhhpro

messages.content: I'm originally from Italy, but I've lived in the UK for a while now. What about you?
messages.speaker: CIVILIAN_english_civilian_AidWorker(Cargo)-BZNtKP1HXIY

messages.content: Cant remember
messages.speaker: BLUFOR_english_PRIVATE_Autorifleman-1hGanXhhpro

messages.content: Ah, that's alright. Is there anything else you wanted to ask or talk about?
messages.speaker: CIVILIAN_english_civilian_AidWorker(Cargo)-BZNtKP1HXIY

messages.content: Yeah, how can I get to Kamino firing range?
messages.speaker: BLUFOR_english_PRIVATE_Autorifleman-1hGanXhhpro

messages.content: Kamino firing range is located to the southeast of Agia Marina. Just head in that direction and you should see signs for it.
messages.speaker: CIVILIAN_english_civilian_AidWorker(Cargo)-BZNtKP1HXIY

messages.content: what about Air station mike 26?
messages.speaker: BLUFOR_english_PRIVATE_Autorifleman-1hGanXhhpro

messages.content: Air Station Mike 26 is located further south from Kamino firing range. Take the main road heading south, and you'll see signs for it.
messages.speaker: CIVILIAN_english_civilian_AidWorker(Cargo)-BZNtKP1HXIY

messages.content: Id like to go see the spartan, do you know where that one is located?
messages.speaker: BLUFOR_english_PRIVATE_Autorifleman-1hGanXhhpro

messages.content: The Spartan is located northeast of Agia Marina. Follow the road that heads in that direction and you'll see signs for it.
messages.speaker: CIVILIAN_english_civilian_AidWorker(Cargo)-BZNtKP1HXIY

messages.content: bullshit, the spartan is located at the southern tip of stratis
messages.speaker: BLUFOR_english_PRIVATE_Autorifleman-1hGanXhhpro

messages.content: I'm sorry, I must have given you incorrect information. The Spartan is actually located at the southern tip of Stratis.
messages.speaker: CIVILIAN_english_civilian_AidWorker(Cargo)-BZNtKP1HXIY

messages.content: Ok so now you can give me the direction to the spartan?
messages.speaker: BLUFOR_english_PRIVATE_Autorifleman-1hGanXhhpro

messages.content: Head south to the tip of Stratis. Signs there will guide you to the Spartan.
messages.speaker: CIVILIAN_english_civilian_AidWorker(Cargo)-BZNtKP1HXIY

messages.content: Hey! How's it hanging?
messages.speaker: BLUFOR_english_PRIVATE_Autorifleman-1hGanXhhpro

messages.content: 'My legs are injured, it's difficult to move. What's going on? Are you okay?'
messages.speaker: CIVILIAN_english_civilian_AidWorker(Cargo)-BZNtKP1HXIY

messages.content: Let me see if I can fix you up, I got a medkit on me
messages.speaker: BLUFOR_english_PRIVATE_Autorifleman-1hGanXhhpro

messages.content: 'Thank you, I appreciate it. What's happening? Why are you guys here? Is everything okay?'
messages.speaker: CIVILIAN_english_civilian_AidWorker(Cargo)-BZNtKP1HXIY

messages.content: Any better?
messages.speaker: BLUFOR_english_PRIVATE_Autorifleman-1hGanXhhpro

messages.content: Yes, thank you. Can you tell me what's happening? My legs don't allow me to move very well.
messages.speaker: CIVILIAN_english_civilian_AidWorker(Cargo)-BZNtKP1HXIY

messages.content: you got shot by the enemy of mankind
messages.speaker: BLUFOR_english_PRIVATE_Autorifleman-1hGanXhhpro

messages.content: I see. That's unfortunate. I hope you catch whoever did it. I might be able to help you guys out if you need it, I have some engineering skills that could come in handy.
messages.speaker: CIVILIAN_english_civilian_AidWorker(Cargo)-BZNtKP1HXIY

messages.content: do you have the time?
messages.speaker: BLUFOR_english_PRIVATE_Autorifleman-1hGanXhhpro

messages.content: Yes, it's currently 12:05. Is there something I can assist you with, Tally?
messages.speaker: CIVILIAN_english_civilian_AidWorker(Cargo)-BZNtKP1HXIY

messages.content: How long until sunset?
messages.speaker: BLUFOR_english_PRIVATE_Autorifleman-1hGanXhhpro

messages.content: Sunset is in approximately three hours, Tally. Is everything okay? You seem a bit tense.
messages.speaker: CIVILIAN_english_civilian_AidWorker(Cargo)-BZNtKP1HXIY

messages.content: Yeah, were looking for a infiltrator
messages.speaker: BLUFOR_english_PRIVATE_Autorifleman-1hGanXhhpro

messages.content: I hope everything turns out okay, Tally. If there's anything I can do to assist, please don't hesitate to ask.
messages.speaker: CIVILIAN_english_civilian_AidWorker(Cargo)-BZNtKP1HXIY

messages.content: Do you know a man named Gerasimos?
messages.speaker: BLUFOR_english_PRIVATE_Autorifleman-1hGanXhhpro

messages.content: Yes, Gerasimos Isofidou. He's a local fisherman here. I haven't seen him in a few days though, have you asked the other locals?
messages.speaker: CIVILIAN_english_civilian_AidWorker(Cargo)-BZNtKP1HXIY

messages.content: Nope, I'll go do that now
messages.speaker: BLUFOR_english_PRIVATE_Autorifleman-1hGanXhhpro

messages.content: Yeah, I heard he might have gone on a fishing trip. I hope you find him soon, Tally. Let me know if you need any more help.
messages.speaker: CIVILIAN_english_civilian_AidWorker(Cargo)-BZNtKP1HXIY
